query:
SELECT
            (
                SELECT COUNT(*)
                FROM tickets
                WHERE created_at >= NOW() - INTERVAL '1 day'
            ) AS "daily_tickets!",
            COUNT(*) AS "tickets_count!",
            CASE
                WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN 0
                ELSE (COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE status = $1)::float / COUNT(*) * 100)
            END AS "percent_of_closed!: f64"
            FROM tickets
